668
00:27:00,240 --> 00:27:01,360
When she didn't have a boyfriend,

669
00:27:01,360 --> 00:27:03,520
I did it to help spread the word.

670
00:27:03,800 --> 00:27:05,320
Now that she's got a boyfriend

671
00:27:05,520 --> 00:27:06,240
and if

