724
00:29:13,960 --> 00:29:14,520
Everything about her is good.

725
00:29:16,360 --> 00:29:17,200
That's so classic.

726
00:29:17,840 --> 00:29:19,040
I'll put this

727
00:29:19,080 --> 00:29:20,000
